Step 1: sudo mv ubuntu-spinner-logo /usr/share/plymouth/themes

Step 2: sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/share/plymouth/themes/default.plymouth default.plymouth /usr/share/plymouth/themes/ubuntu-spinner-logo/ubuntu-spinner-logo.plymouth 200

Step 3: sudo update-alternatives --config default.plymouth

Step 4: Select ubuntu-spinner-logo either 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 ect......

Step 5: sudo update-initramfs -u

Background can easily be replaced with a background of your choice :-)
